an work safely and effectively.\",\"Proactive planning - Being punctual having the van and equipment ready and anticipating the needs of the team are essential to keeping our passengers and freight moving.\",\"Working under pressure - Working outdoors in all conditions and with trains passing close by means you�ll need to remain calm under pressure.\",\"Following rules and instructions - It is important that you understand and respect the rules but also feel confident to challenge if you see a situation is unsafe.\",\"Willingness to learn - You�ll consistently develop your skills and competencies relevant to your discipline keeping up to date with new standards procedures and instructions.\"],\"desirable\":[],\"keyAccountabilities\":[]}  }"